ve their skills.\", \"from\": 447, \"to\": 535, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Two Mason High School students helped with marketing for this year's event.\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 612, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 541, \"end\": 558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Mason_High_School_(Mason,_Ohio)\", \"score\": 0.6327683596700655, \"rank\": 0.43750000000003797, \"text\": \"Mason High School\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3914\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Mason_High_School_(Mason,_Ohio)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Mason_High_School_(Mason,_Ohio)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Main thing being able to give opportunities to students in the tech field is really important because it's really hard to find those if you do not have the connections or the people and just the events to show you those opportunities,\\\" explained Jajoo Ananya.\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 874, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 867, \"end\": 873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ananya_Panday\", \"score\": 0.9973447326651598, \"rank\": 0.0026623365389918437, \"text\": \"Ananya\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ananya_Panday\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ananya_Panday\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel like a lot of my friends are scared to talk about tech or be in to it, so just getting them to come to events like this to that its more it's not as intimidating as it might seem at first is really valuable i think,\\\" added Estelle Apewokin.\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 1124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1107, \"end\": 1114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Estelle_Getty\", \"score\": 0.9690769062597155, \"rank\": 0.031909820192096205, \"text\": \"Estelle\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Estelle_Getty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Estelle_Get